{"tid":1183313,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[live] (長氣多圖） 獨遊意大利，瑞士，荷蘭11日","createTime":"2019-06-02T22:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T08:50:43.000Z","uid":69174,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"41146b18c869b896dfa81fe789ce50863b5a445c","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T22:53:59.000Z","msg":"［長氣，多圖］ 歐遊22天<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1174397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1174397</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n跟住落嚟係獨遊11日 <br />\n有興趣嘅可以睇返我前11日同fd去玩嘅post<br />\n<br />\n因為同fd已經分開左<br />\n感覺上自己1個人時間都多左<br />\n獨遊會覺得有啲無聊<br />\n所以想開新post 係live<br />\n可以keep住更新自己近況<br />\n行度邊影到邊<br />\n舊post都會keep住一直出落去<br />\n<br />\n暫定主要行程<br />\nDay 11 Mykonos paradise beach<br />\nDay 12 Mykonos to 威尼斯 by airport、Murano 玻璃島、<br />\nBurano 彩色島、聖馬可廣場、嘆息橋、學院橋<br />\n<br />\nDay 13 威尼斯本島、搭貢多尼遊威尼斯、<br />\n搭火車由威尼斯去米蘭<br />\n<br />\nDay 14 米蘭主座教堂、埃馬努埃二世拱廊、<br />\nMilano to Interlaken by train、哈德昆景觀臺<br />\n<br />\nDay 15 (Swiss) 少女峰與雪朗峰、去Luzern、<br />\n卡貝爾橋、冰河公園、垂死獅子像<br />\nDay 16 鐵力士峰、Stanserhorn Bahn、Engelberg、石丹峰、搭火車去蘇黎世<br />\nDay 17 蘇黎世內行下，Rhine Falls                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           <br />\nDay 18 蘇黎世搭飛機去Amsterdam、<br />\nAlbert Cuypmarkt、紅燈區<br />\n<br />\nDay 19 (Holland) 羊角村<br />\nDay 20 桑斯安斯風車村、Amsterdam to Rotterdam by train<br />\nDay 21 小孩堤防，方塊屋<br />\nDay 22 Rotterdam to Brussel by train，<br />\n再喺Brussel行下，搭飛機返香港 <br />\n<br />\n因為之前嘅10日歐洲之旅幾乎9日都係藍天白雲<br />\n希望之後都可以keep住係咁樣 <br />\n而且唔會再發生咩意外啦<br />\n例如唔好整唔見毛巾同埋電話卡<br />\n<br />\n理想圖 （圖片由google提供）<br />\n<br />\n威尼斯本島<br />\n<img src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1295,h_720,f_auto/w_80,x_15,y_15,g_south_west,l_klook_water/activities/jxtynrrh1kil7c7akka7/%E8%B2%A2%E5%A4%9A%E6%8B%89%E8%88%B9%E9%81%8A%E5%A8%81%E5%B0%BC%E6%96%AF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fres.klook.com%2Fimages%2Ffl_lossy.progressive%2Cq_65%2Fc_fill%2Cw_1295%2Ch_720%2Cf_auto%2Fw_80%2Cx_15%2Cy_15%2Cg_south_west%2Cl_klook_water%2Factivities%2Fjxtynrrh1kil7c7akka7%2F%25E8%25B2%25A2%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%258B%2589%25E8%2588%25B9%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25A8%2581%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E6%2596%25AF.jpg&h=92cdfcb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彩色島<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.venuslin.tw/uploads/20170711105208_82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.venuslin.tw%2Fuploads%2F20170711105208_82.jpg&h=c524e1a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n米蘭主座教堂<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/ooaboo/1444241740-78782679_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fooaboo%2F1444241740-78782679_l.jpg&h=dce94371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nInterlaken<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/jay7134/1467394854-20094917_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fjay7134%2F1467394854-20094917_l.jpg&h=dddb4fed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n少女峰<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.daisyyohoho.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jungfrau-131.jpg?fit=1000%2C668&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.daisyyohoho.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2Fjungfrau-131.jpg%3Ffit%3D1000%252C668%26ssl%3D1&h=b7cf8647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雪朗峰<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.daisyyohoho.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/schilthorn-146.jpg?resize=1000%2C667\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.daisyyohoho.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fschilthorn-146.jpg%3Fresize%3D1000%252C667&h=a83f532d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLuzern<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.luzern.com/fileadmin/user_upload/Luzern_Tourismus/Bilder/Highlights/Die_Stadt/Kapellbruecke/kapellbruecke-wasserturm-sehenswuerdigkeit-luzern_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.luzern.com%2Ffileadmin%2Fuser_upload%2FLuzern_Tourismus%2FBilder%2FHighlights%2FDie_Stadt%2FKapellbruecke%2Fkapellbruecke-wasserturm-sehenswuerdigkeit-luzern_1.jpg&h=935b9357&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"869fbd24c2b491dc4157b808425712c484e3988a","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T22:54:14.000Z","msg":"鐵力士峰<br />\n<img src=\"http://s5.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0025u2uazy76auO7bQUa4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs5.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F0025u2uazy76auO7bQUa4&h=94b49edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n石丹峰<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.daisyyohoho.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/stans-2.jpg?resize=1000%2C667&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.daisyyohoho.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Fstans-2.jpg%3Fresize%3D1000%252C667%26ssl%3D1&h=82600eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘇黎世<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.daisyyohoho.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/zurich-143.jpg?fit=1100%2C735&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.daisyyohoho.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2Fzurich-143.jpg%3Ffit%3D1100%252C735%26ssl%3D1&h=3b7d7cf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRhine Falls<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.switzerland-tours.ch/media/k2/items/cache/e9c724eeb5636d1c1c1a2c2e85d40377_XL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.switzerland-tours.ch%2Fmedia%2Fk2%2Fitems%2Fcache%2Fe9c724eeb5636d1c1c1a2c2e85d40377_XL.jpg&h=ed254feb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAmsterdam<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.iamexpat.nl/sites/default/files/styles/article--full/public/rijksmuseum-amsterdam-museum-iamsterdam.jpg?itok=MwiTROHQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iamexpat.nl%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Farticle--full%2Fpublic%2Frijksmuseum-amsterdam-museum-iamsterdam.jpg%3Fitok%3DMwiTROHQ&h=e1e51404&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羊角村<br />\n<img src=\"https://wecallbad.files.wordpress.com/2015/10/dsc_0656.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwecallbad.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F10%2Fdsc_0656.jpg&h=ef37a6d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n桑斯安斯風車村<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.picturesinthekoaframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/13-4-1080x720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.picturesinthekoaframe.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F13-4-1080x720.jpg&h=15d4ef19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小孩堤防<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/hoyaplanet/1517655590-136276473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fhoyaplanet%2F1517655590-136276473.jpg&h=90cb0fa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRotterdam<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thetimes.co.uk/imageserver/image/methode%2Ftimes%2Fprod%2Fweb%2Fbin%2Fbc901afe-3c05-11e8-b6d1-2c479ec10e4b.jpg?crop=5219%2C2936%2C26%2C525&amp;resize=685\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Fimageserver%2Fimage%2Fmethode%252Ftimes%252Fprod%252Fweb%252Fbin%252Fbc901afe-3c05-11e8-b6d1-2c479ec10e4b.jpg%3Fcrop%3D5219%252C2936%252C26%252C525%26resize%3D685&h=e7d59672&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"925f12927b6ccaadd074faa095892be22c3204b6","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T23:09:37.000Z","msg":"Day 11 Mykonos paradise beach<br />\n<br />\n搭巴士去paradise beach嘅辦法係<br />\n喺舊港度搭巴士過去<br />\n每半小時一班車<br />\n4.5歐單程1個人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4akSewr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4akSewr.png&h=bcd9f054&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o2Wqzwv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo2Wqzwv.png&h=fd96c297&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bFUPgK6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbFUPgK6.png&h=a8c09125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日都係依舊藍天白雲嘅好天氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且比起琴日熱<br />\n希望今次到paradise beach可以見到裸女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://  na.cx/i/YmbNNSa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F%20%20na.cx%2Fi%2FYmbNNSa.png&h=df90968e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車上面竟然淨係得我一個人<br />\n喺車上面我以為唔見左副太陽眼鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚇到我諗住要返轉頭搵返<br />\n好采喺前面座位搵返<br />\n原來係頭先比錢隨便咁放低左副黑超喺位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n酒店係paradise beach resort<br />\n1晚要57.5歐1個人<br />\n真係好貴 不過太遲訂 早2個月先訂廿<br />\n而且訂嘅當時睇極都唔明mykonos啲交通<br />\n見呢度1個人1間房 比起其他要平啲就訂左呢度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7CfZD0U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7CfZD0U.png&h=1fa77935&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zz8wu7X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZz8wu7X.png&h=447bbb5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S7xk7UG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS7xk7UG.png&h=c942090d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b4rRu76.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb4rRu76.png&h=7361b248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n房間係細左啲<br />\n不過都可以接受<br />\n馬桶嘅沖水力係我嚟左歐洲咁耐最好嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能近沙灘海水唔洗慳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7MUGSzY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7MUGSzY.png&h=3af51efa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dLwFoGH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdLwFoGH.png&h=942dc718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為喺度嘅沙灘椅係要收錢嘅<br />\n為左慳返之前豪洗同喺酒店用左嘅錢<br />\n就喺餐廳叫啲野食坐喺餐廳入面算<br />\n叫左肉醬意粉 10歐 加一杯雲尼拿奶昔5歐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PZUDamK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPZUDamK.png&h=194ab67b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7JGNN8u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7JGNN8u.png&h=50050384&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DkHtxAb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDkHtxAb.png&h=5f213440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年嘅天體沙灘<br />\n幾乎已經冇人會再除哂衫曬太陽<br />\n我喺度逗留左接近5個鐘<br />\n見到個阿婆除左上身bar之外<br />\n就見到有個靚女除左bar趴喺度曬太陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋有個男人除埋底褲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a1igGty.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa1igGty.png&h=4d3c37aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtzGSAf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtzGSAf.png&h=7da06174&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9carjfj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9carjfj.png&h=23b4aa13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NaFiUOJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNaFiUOJ.png&h=63e8f83e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚 去mini market 買左支zero 1.1歐<br />\n1包薯片2歐 同1包M&amp;M 1.5歐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GP4ceQK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGP4ceQK.png&h=fdd46f7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後返去沙灘今日中午食個間restaurant <br />\n叫左個4 seasons pizza 12歐<br />\nPizza個皮係軟脆嘅<br />\n不過冇咩特別<br />\n就係食到我好飽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rou35Xs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frou35Xs.png&h=624f23dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kh03mvW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkh03mvW.png&h=e2d4d568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jH2hqXD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjH2hqXD.png&h=fe94b58b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KY6NOa1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKY6NOa1.png&h=ba597667&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pp3AcCS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPp3AcCS.png&h=c7cb5d90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚嘅paradise beach 都仲係好多人<br />\n啲bar大概由3點鐘開始播歌<br />\n會有啲sexy ladies喺度跳舞 帶動啲氣氛<br />\n我就嫌佢個音響開得太嘈<br />\n返房打下機算"},{"pid":"278466cef8d99fe40846b058ab278827d81fee02","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T23:11:48.000Z","msg":"而家就2點鐘 準備瞓教<br />\n聽朝7點鐘起身食個快嘅酒店早餐<br />\n然後焗住搭的士去機場<br />\n因為班去威尼斯嘅機係0955<br />\n而我仲要搞托運<br />\n最遲最遲都要0855到<br />\n雖然機場好近 離酒店得10分鐘車程<br />\n希望冇意外啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fab6413f6eb5756f7e397328d51e7e8f4803f0f","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wqz37PL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWqz37PL.png&h=f43d3387&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fp3TLBs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffp3TLBs.png&h=1b251453&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fqr2DWv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqr2DWv.png&h=a5105b44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2AGRxgx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2AGRxgx.png&h=c480ed4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱起身開始食早餐<br />\n今餐係酒店費入面包埋嘅"},{"pid":"14d9ade5a6838ee7bcd4a4a0c437a07baaeab1b7","tid":1183313,"uid":129182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fab6413f6eb5756f7e397328d51e7e8f4803f0f","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wqz37PL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWqz37PL.png&h=f43d3387&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fp3TLBs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffp3TLBs.png&h=1b251453&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fqr2DWv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqr2DWv.png&h=a5105b44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2AGRxgx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2AGRxgx.png&h=c480ed4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱起身開始食早餐<br />\n今餐係酒店費入面包埋嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />肉全部都係肉"},{"pid":"d722f0d5f371ae4372ee12b8be0c901ccf28d131","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oDeWJAz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoDeWJAz.png&h=13cba2ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMFOzHj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMFOzHj.png&h=07441866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為太早嘅關係 先得8點鐘<br />\n冇巴士係可以出去機場<br />\n唯有靠酒店嘅接駁車<br />\n車我出機場 要成20歐<br />\n其實車程只有10mins 3km<br />\n雖然話搭巴士出去要轉車<br />\n都要5歐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oY4WJDD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoY4WJDD.png&h=9dee7629&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rfUPjcj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrfUPjcj.png&h=b352ab3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左搭廉航去威尼斯用左29歐<br />\n但係因為我發覺佢個個hand baggage<br />\n淨係包到我個20吋gip<br />\n個大袋原全oversize<br />\n最後提早比左40歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果要on board先知<br />\n就要成60歐<br />\n仲貴過程機 痴撚線<br />\n下次去歐洲我會帶少啲衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd20b2f51c2d2ce44bf621f99d34644927b98786","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X0SEGUe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX0SEGUe.png&h=0b5a0f2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MZZS1Ug.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMZZS1Ug.png&h=bf7f27ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等左比預期耐嘅20分鐘 <br />\n終於上到飛機<br />\n希望喺上面都唔好delay太耐<br />\n同埋到威尼斯都係咁好天<br />\n查左當地天氣預報係太陽加陰天"},{"pid":"ed8f579dbb17d5f21476f8d9647bb92b9b7d2a32","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:17:00.000Z","msg":"推遲左40分鐘 終於肯飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hg4zvVi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHg4zvVi.png&h=175af8b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"523f1659c2b7850b408be1c7ca96ebc76470a041","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T10:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WAfgnd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WAfgnd.png&h=6bf1a01a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3rmWne.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3rmWne.png&h=2cc7ba40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於到埗<br />\n計返時差嘅話 都飛左成2個幾鐘<br />\n由機場買1 day pass for water transport<br />\n再加單程由機場出市區<br />\n要成26歐<br />\n之後一路跟住指示 就可以到碼頭等船<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GPqCuHh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGPqCuHh.png&h=83bc303e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZ5rn2k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZ5rn2k.png&h=4b024e13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78DHFO4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78DHFO4.png&h=77a4fe63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實由機場去返威尼斯本島<br />\n或者酒店都幾遠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MD195gS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMD195gS.png&h=128e9e97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2ef28b791aa01c41807d698d94ac6da9c33eafe","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T10:48:09.000Z","msg":"已經炒左車<br />\n買嘅26歐係for巴士去<br />\n然後水上巴士1 day pas<br />\n如果想搭船唔洗轉車同行咁多路<br />\n應該要買嘅係就咁1日pass<br />\n同埋單程出去15歐<br />\n結果而家要轉車靠搭船去<br />\n最慘係頭先冇數據<br />\n我咩都查唔到<br />\n焗住要買票<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KJFSiLp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKJFSiLp.png&h=2676605b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDoTNDL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDoTNDL.png&h=4a35026c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5cb91fa824397bbf068196f1e88bbc76f8ec5b49","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T11:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JkBieAx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJkBieAx.png&h=24c427d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hB8gLHg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhB8gLHg.png&h=1a5e25eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFqu5Hn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFqu5Hn.png&h=0f54c641&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FgHmcnq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFgHmcnq.png&h=817cb2fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總算落左巴士<br />\n跟住要行一小段路去碼頭<br />\n爭啲搞錯左方向<br />\n不過啲碼頭指示好清楚<br />\n有show埋邊條線係咩英文字母碼頭<br />\n仲有到站時間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EWfu5Jj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEWfu5Jj.png&h=55975fbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bccad877651903147aaf841ba8eb29d590206a06","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T14:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cqpzxQS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcqpzxQS.png&h=dc245cca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ntVZJXC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FntVZJXC.png&h=bb7fbb38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZa68pk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZa68pk.png&h=fd56dc37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行左一段路 <br />\n1405 終於到酒店<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DXZ7SQ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDXZ7SQ3.png&h=c8eaf022&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YrcJra6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYrcJra6.png&h=eafb24ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n酒店房都算唔錯<br />\n係唔知點解夾萬用唔到<br />\n不過1個人住真係好貴同唔抵<br />\n要成63歐再加3歐city tax<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XsPDe4v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXsPDe4v.png&h=4f898fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KjePmKx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKjePmKx.png&h=dd2a92a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後搭船去玻璃島<br />\n因為見到有船就跳左上去先<br />\n雖然係同一個number<br />\n但係其實係2條線<br />\n我應該搭個條係應該環線咁樣繞到玻璃島<br />\n<br />\n唯有喺下一個站搭返過去<br />\n再睇返清楚個站往嘅方向有冇Murano 先上"},{"pid":"e686c38fd5414f44497f90067f48aa5c3d3aa995","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T16:56:37.000Z","msg":"Day 12 Murano<br />\n<br />\n我嘅酒店離碼頭好近<br />\n而個碼頭離玻璃島只有2個站<br />\n望都望到<br />\n唔洗10分鐘就到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0euDfCw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0euDfCw.png&h=d722deca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Vgeype.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Vgeype.png&h=50eac6bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dC38CQX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdC38CQX.png&h=da6c0ed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到左玻璃島<br />\n幾乎周圍都係呢啲玻璃製嘅商店<br />\n又或者係一啲整燈嘅鋪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FEcEKv0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFEcEKv0.png&h=a9073c19&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddvnHhK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FddvnHhK.png&h=a4ec2f45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qaz4ba6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQaz4ba6.png&h=ca24dfad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為都已經3點幾<br />\n又唔太想入餐廳食<br />\n就去左間超市買法包食<br />\n同埋買2支zero飲<br />\n加埋2.5歐<br />\n其實如果有帶水樽<br />\n就唔洗買野飲<br />\n因為周圍都有水龍頭比你斟水飲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFpS4wb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFpS4wb.png&h=af118a27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後都搵左間鋪買啲玻璃杯<br />\n見呢間特別平<br />\n買個細杯先6歐<br />\n其他都係10歐一個<br />\n入去揀左個聖誕製品 <br />\n入面有個雪人加聖誕樹 7歐<br />\n再加多2個杯 每個6歐<br />\n最後老闆娘仲好好人咁叫我喺啲首飾揀個<br />\n揀左個心形 可以套落條蠅度<br />\n真係覺得冇揀錯鋪頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CJxxj4G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCJxxj4G.png&h=62ce134e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9NVu6KK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9NVu6KK.png&h=7b262a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BcK0uFX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBcK0uFX.png&h=697dbdca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都圍左個島走成個鐘 <br />\n雖然冇走哂<br />\n但都叫行左6、7成<br />\n其實全部都係啲賣玻璃嘅鋪頭<br />\n或者係餐廳<br />\n而我對玻璃製品表演又冇咩興趣<br />\n就搭船過去彩虹島 上船嘅時候係1630"},{"pid":"a38df4361dab62d71dec22655f5c114a2ffb89d5","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:04:18.000Z","msg":"Day 12 Burano <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00EG3NY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00EG3NY.png&h=0cc2d092&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一落船 直入行會見到間賣畫嘅鋪頭<br />\n1幅細嘅畫大概都係7-10歐<br />\n因為想睇左啲彩虹屋先再決定買唔買<br />\n就繼續向前行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aWVV8eF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaWVV8eF.png&h=8c67c676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路向前行直到見到座橋<br />\n個度係網上面話最好影相嘅地點<br />\n一列整齊彩虹屋再加上倒影喺河上嘅影像<br />\n真係幾靚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tVe0zUH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtVe0zUH.png&h=c9c2f000&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y8D1jmp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy8D1jmp.png&h=2c58b508&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BBFbGzL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBBFbGzL.png&h=e51a14a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QXoHOeN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXoHOeN.png&h=b2b131fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ib62OeP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fib62OeP.png&h=c376a983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路行落去 都會見到有各式各類嘅彩虹屋<br />\n基本上成個小鎮都係咁<br />\n如果屋主想改自己間屋嘅顏色<br />\n仲要同政府申請先得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N6BNZsZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN6BNZsZ.png&h=fe05315c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1間特別少少嘅彩虹屋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Q6RGGm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Q6RGGm.png&h=18f8a9e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4QkyU1o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4QkyU1o.png&h=fd561667&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBurano 仲有第二個特色係賣蕾絲嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmcJxN5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmcJxN5.png&h=76f2d8c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLgyazN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLgyazN.png&h=dfc25695&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5qjjQzO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5qjjQzO.png&h=d3cc0db7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實除左上面嘅Love viewing bridge 之外<br />\n其實其他地方都可以影埋倒影<br />\n不過都要好天氣配合先得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TvGeEt7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTvGeEt7.png&h=33393b45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後返到嚟都買左10歐一幅畫<br />\n7歐嘅雖然細啲同平啲<br />\n但佢係瓷磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲重<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ynBFz2w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FynBFz2w.png&h=3d93b962&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過喺第二間度搵到幅好靚嘅<br />\n喺頭先個間見唔到<br />\n都係7歐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcwqL89.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxcwqL89.png&h=a6bf8fdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8DKf8oS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8DKf8oS.png&h=175f2a60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨走前喺碼頭前面見到個咁狂野嘅石像<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vs5ZQCe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvs5ZQCe.png&h=02e9eca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n彩虹島同玻璃島上面有好多呢啲水龍頭<br />\n有時周圍啲人都會圍住嚟斟水<br />\n不過喺威尼斯本島就唔覺有"},{"pid":"a6460eb6b3a915e2ea87072e599a59a1bba2ea12","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"Day 12 Venezia<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcygSVC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtcygSVC.png&h=5cacce6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實喺本島都有好多鋪係賣返玻璃島鋪賣嘅野<br />\n有啲貴過但都有啲係平嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EWDD6fE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEWDD6fE.png&h=e7dd3449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h8ogSVG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh8ogSVG.png&h=99c7ad1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s6nUEAJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs6nUEAJ.png&h=d81cd35f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出到去聖馬可廣場 真係比布魯塞爾個個大好大<br />\n仲要更加宏偉<br />\n難怪連拿破崙都讚佢係歐洲最美嘅客廳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gwhEQHq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgwhEQHq.png&h=dc9391cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxChCns.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxChCns.png&h=a84cbda8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QsO1jAP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQsO1jAP.png&h=64004a01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺廣場隔離 就係嘆息橋<br />\n以前啲犯人就係條橋入面入去坐牢<br />\n就係臨入嘅時候<br />\n因為條橋就得幾個小洞可以望返出嚟<br />\n傳說都話啲犯人會不自禁咁喺度嘆息<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GhVbGPa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGhVbGPa.png&h=912cc55b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHYgSVT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHYgSVT.png&h=f824ae29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣場入面有好多雀<br />\n仲會有人喺度引你餵食啲雀<br />\n就喺你前面餵啲雀去引你<br />\n目測一定要比錢 所以就搖頭說不<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/04/171933_dff6ca8f36b308660a15eba2e1c1eff9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F04%2F171933_dff6ca8f36b308660a15eba2e1c1eff9.png&h=4cbd62d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後行左10分鐘嘅路去學院橋<br />\n因為聽講喺度適合睇日落<br />\n可以欣賞埋安康聖母聖殿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZX9G5ow.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZX9G5ow.png&h=53f0d6a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QsWKiJy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQsWKiJy.png&h=fdc287d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mj0bJae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMj0bJae.png&h=acd632b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BtaV9Qg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBtaV9Qg.png&h=faa4fbed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9wsQYJD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9wsQYJD.png&h=a3aac402&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後搭返船返廣場<br />\n打算去食呢間Caffe Florian<br />\n係威尼斯最早嘅咖啡館<br />\n入面裝潢好豪華<br />\n但係因為見到又要比音樂表演費<br />\n再加服務費<br />\n而且疑似佢只係開到十點<br />\n去到嘅時候都2140<br />\n所以都係放棄左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ytQeip.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ytQeip.png&h=b374149c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBHYobW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvBHYobW.png&h=df594e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JkJ1kYG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJkJ1kYG.png&h=b589fc42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cvWm5qq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcvWm5qq.png&h=18d5d235&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zz0OLqt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZz0OLqt.png&h=4769c39d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SVr2PTs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSVr2PTs.png&h=d62457db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ji66w7m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fji66w7m.png&h=d14fade9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到9點整嘅時候 <br />\n鐘塔上面2個人像會敲響個鐘報時<br />\n<br />\n原先諗住去食左晚餐先 再返嚟睇夜景<br />\n但最後太攰同已經行左返酒店附近食<br />\n就放棄左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RsSp3du.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRsSp3du.png&h=3a440fd4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHNtLrU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHNtLrU.png&h=14103da8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/enyTWyC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FenyTWyC.png&h=0516b31e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WCpWUmW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWCpWUmW.png&h=b29fb88d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後呢餐食左25歐<br />\n20係main course <br />\n3歐芬達<br />\n同2歐服務費<br />\n個魷魚其實幾好食 熱辣辣<br />\n仲要入面係有料嘅<br />\n就係貴左少少"},{"pid":"85cb44dc25e863ba2a0dcbb8cf24af18f9c20871","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T17:31:14.000Z","msg":"Day 13 Gondola tour <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BATT5hJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBATT5hJ.png&h=cec9bc84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係琴日嘅budget <br />\n估唔到食少左一餐都抵消唔到<br />\n錢主要洗哂係住同搭車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oSMRRbb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoSMRRbb.png&h=958e56cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g6gqVCT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg6gqVCT.png&h=87b09798&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fMNUOXW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfMNUOXW.png&h=8ffed998&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKRyj4F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKRyj4F.png&h=399bb823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朝早9點半起身<br />\n因為10點就要check out<br />\n不過時間都差唔多<br />\n因為我book左11點嘅貢多拉tour<br />\n所以就出左大廣場行轉<br />\n喺隔離買左3歐2球雪糕食下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2MeOX5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2MeOX5.png&h=68ba3e58&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OVds8X8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOVds8X8.png&h=3e731d82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貢多拉嘅集合地點係喺附近嘅郵局隔離<br />\n呢個貢多拉係我喺klook 度訂返嚟<br />\n都要成30歐 6人一架船<br />\n雖然網上面話會有著藍色衫嘅工作人員<br />\n但結果係黑衫同白衫<br />\n會比張貼紙你做記認<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xjs5VDa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXjs5VDa.png&h=2901656e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gQbVypT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgQbVypT.png&h=6ade0290&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQjjZ4V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQjjZ4V.png&h=78874f12&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XWvjfDi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXWvjfDi.png&h=a1a72f40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行左一段路同排一陣隊<br />\n就可以正式用貢多拉遊威尼斯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/stG6GkD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FstG6GkD.png&h=4fc32cdd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KgFvoy0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKgFvoy0.png&h=65ca5f72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5OEgT2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5OEgT2.png&h=ca952b95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYGuD7p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYGuD7p.png&h=c5d517b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iq0nY7r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiq0nY7r.png&h=9a6574e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實就咁坐喺船上面搖下搖下<br />\n睇下個景<br />\n澳門威尼斯人都真係有幾分似威尼斯<br />\n個藍天白雲真係幾近<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VPHhN0N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPHhN0N.png&h=b04d9af1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CcBi7u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CcBi7u.png&h=298a4d22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jU7Bi7w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjU7Bi7w.png&h=4dce089b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QsarGkS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQsarGkS.png&h=f959bab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實覺得今次貢多拉唔抵<br />\n係因為佢只係帶你兜左個圈<br />\n真係啱啱好30分鐘<br />\n但就唔會經過嘆息橋之類嘅景點<br />\n所以如果人多嘅話或者唔介意錢<br />\n真係可以自己包隻船<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o7a3JEz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo7a3JEz.png&h=aa123d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bsgVzMh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbsgVzMh.png&h=43d73fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5EcE1rj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5EcE1rj.png&h=476801d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qk7NqS0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqk7NqS0.png&h=856fa602&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1036a5fa3db7ad24d89f2f4f285b76b863f301e","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T05:27:20.000Z","msg":"Day 13 Venezia to Milano<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98u4s7h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98u4s7h.png&h=00a3df84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5oMKs7j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5oMKs7j.png&h=63759e32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NPnQ77m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNPnQ77m.png&h=58491504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨出發塊米蘭之前<br />\n喺度要買返啲面具做手信<br />\n1個大嘅7歐<br />\n就咁遮眼嘅3歐1個<br />\n遮哂成塊面就10歐1個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXn5W0K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXn5W0K.png&h=7174aea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後求其見到間bar<br />\n就買個6歐嘅包食<br />\n見攰諗住去廣場坐下<br />\n點知比隻雀空中襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一腳踢我隻手<br />\n搞到我成個包飛左出去<br />\n喺廣場度大嗌左一聲屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f31RSy6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff31RSy6.png&h=0450f509&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHsJJFO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHsJJFO.png&h=ea3d4754&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ryNmvkQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FryNmvkQ.png&h=e0bc1b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ONLWjec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FONLWjec.png&h=92dca706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再返返去間野買第二個6歐嘅包<br />\n今次就好小心唔行出去<br />\n其實我極懷疑啲雀全部喺度低飛都係搵獵物<br />\n仲應該有唔少嘅受害者<br />\n建議大家食野唔好出廣場 好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ytQoHL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ytQoHL.png&h=e3be5487&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vVd5cA7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvVd5cA7.png&h=9db9eee3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jAbB3HP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjAbB3HP.png&h=ef379801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n返酒店拎返啲行李之前<br />\n因為天氣真係太熱<br />\n買左杯雲呢拿嘅奶昔4.5歐<br />\n但係杯野太濃<br />\n唔太鍾意飲 飲完仲有啲口渴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocEsqWb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocEsqWb.png&h=1325a044&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/20fCN9z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F20fCN9z.png&h=d256ab34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zuKsqWf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzuKsqWf.png&h=88ad56a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為1 day pass應該用完<br />\n而且行都唔係比搭船遠好多<br />\n唯二辛苦嘅就係天氣熱<br />\n同威尼斯真係要過好多橋<br />\n橋仲要大部分都冇設計比行李嘅<br />\n得1道橋有 就係上面個張<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FV3tanX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFV3tanX.png&h=393cf0a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aUmB3HZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaUmB3HZ.png&h=37e5ec19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後搭1520嘅火車過去米蘭<br />\n要23歐<br />\n大概1800到達米蘭中央車站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LRQnZhQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLRQnZhQ.png&h=5fc43518&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pgzj1wc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgzj1wc.png&h=4d39ec36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Cqy5XU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Cqy5XU.png&h=9fc5d691&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K1OQoKC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK1OQoKC.png&h=dcb3693c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e145867ad845c79a0e8285dae0f1acbd45bec99","tid":1183313,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T05:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f6a2fd6c44fac5ca45205eb206ceaf9e84b495","tid":1183313,"uid":41480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"未追post 想知樓主預計用幾多錢同帶幾多錢？"},{"pid":"cc185f49d7406722f41fc3d3aa2771a35a60e01e","tid":1183313,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T05:54:25.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"50d6f46186ca30fe0883006f58e64382b275af03","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2f6a2fd6c44fac5ca45205eb206ceaf9e84b495","tid":1183313,"uid":41480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"未追post 想知樓主預計用幾多錢同帶幾多錢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"唱左15000hkd過去<br />\n其中11000轉歐元 4000轉瑞士法郎<br />\n<br />\n因為初初真係唔知洗幾多<br />\n所以預返每日洗700-800hkd<br />\n唔夠再碌卡<br />\n不過暫時day 14 已經洗左23000 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n計哂暫時為止嘅所有住宿交通 食 買 景點費"},{"pid":"d7da3bfca694b06c225113cd217fd35908b1eedf","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:36:12.000Z","msg":"Day 13 Milano <br />\n<br />\n到米蘭入住嘅係喺中央車站附近嘅係<br />\nOstello Bello Grande<br />\n行過去只需要5分鐘<br />\n43歐1個6人房床位<br />\n不過就包早餐同晚餐<br />\n其實除左係張床冇咩私隱之外<br />\n幾乎都好高質<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iK2mzjg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiK2mzjg.png&h=c1b626ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OhFn3cD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhFn3cD.png&h=fdff1191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一入到嚟check in 嘅時候<br />\n青旅會比杯welcome drink<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hvr23cE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvr23cE.png&h=7ff2533d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚟左歐洲咁多日 終於可以洗衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗同乾加埋要7歐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ohFn3cF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FohFn3cF.png&h=72be6e34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/icvbWxG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FicvbWxG.png&h=49b546da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmASFZn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmASFZn.png&h=157d515f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4hFGzjp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4hFGzjp.png&h=6af2efdd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uJZoNEq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuJZoNEq.png&h=a0d1a6a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQQ7uSM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQQ7uSM.png&h=69dec542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n青旅喺7-9提供晚餐<br />\n其實都算幾多選擇<br />\n為左慳錢唔好再洗咁多<br />\n就喺度食飽先出去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oaJH3Bz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoaJH3Bz.png&h=d9e0bc1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/czE8eJf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FczE8eJf.png&h=08ab89be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mSE4xuX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmSE4xuX.png&h=4e5e4bf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺米蘭搭車其實都幾方便<br />\n我就買左張1day pass 嘅4.5歐<br />\n其實single way 都得<br />\n90分鐘之內都可以獨狂用<br />\n不過既然我第二日都出去<br />\n就買張1day pass"},{"pid":"401a1fedfee0bc13995690cea8b71a3f9e878aa3","tid":1183313,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:38:32.000Z","msg":"好想知day 15點去<br />\n隨意門? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9bbe40ee148e03fc611cf365e37d482f05c9df9","tid":1183313,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:19:42.000Z","msg":"Day 13 Milano<br />\n<br />\n出到嚟嘅時候係2020<br />\n因為喺度日落都比較遲 2100先日落<br />\n可以見到教堂另一面景象<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EvVrLRK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEvVrLRK.png&h=2ef5c2b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJxRcwL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtJxRcwL.png&h=8e862237&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ru3AEbM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRu3AEbM.png&h=8572ec40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zfkfEbN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzfkfEbN.png&h=69ddf1ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hCoH3Dt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhCoH3Dt.png&h=890d2f35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺拱門入面<br />\n傳說中踩住佢睪丸轉一圈<br />\n就會有好運 可以生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周圍都好多人圍住要踩<br />\n可以見到嘅係<br />\n嗰個位甚至比人踩到凹左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYOg8mB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYOg8mB.png&h=d5a85acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1XLCSwR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1XLCSwR.png&h=e6521f6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XONmzLc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXONmzLc.png&h=6337d038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺度遇到手繩黨<br />\n基本上就算佢係咁hi你<br />\n只要唔望佢 唔應佢<br />\n行多陣佢就會唔跟你<br />\n如果唔係就可能佢會套條手繩落你度屈你錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ePGZmVm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FePGZmVm.png&h=9982b37a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zMHYCtJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzMHYCtJ.png&h=bfd9f63d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1EneaOL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1EneaOL.png&h=1f84caea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b1mFQOP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb1mFQOP.png&h=15a4afc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f7eL1Vw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff7eL1Vw.png&h=6a794a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等到去10點 天都總算黑哂<br />\n喺教堂嘅周圍<br />\n屋頂上或者係啲電燈柱<br />\n都會有射燈射落去教堂度<br />\n等佢夜晚嘅時候都可以keep住佢嘅宏偉"}]}